d-play MC UPS™ stabilizes voltage in milliseconds—whole-site protection, fault-tolerant design, UL/NFPA aligned, grid-ready.","7c995c8e-7397-4133-9159-48e57db15b01","Mission-Critical Power Quality ",{"type":196,"content":197},"doc",[198,210,219],{"type":199,"attrs":200,"content":202},"heading",{"level":201,"textAlign":139},3,[203],{"text":204,"type":205,"marks":206},"Trusted by Operators","text",[207],{"type":208,"attrs":209},"textStyle",{"color":18},{"type":211,"attrs":212,"content":213},"paragraph",{"textAlign":139},[214],{"text":215,"type":205,"marks":216},"Deployed in some of the harshest environments, our systems are relied on by large, sophisticated operators with the highest uptime requirements.",[217],{"type":208,"attrs":218},{"color":18},{"type":211,"attrs":220,"content":221},{"textAlign":139},[222],{"text":223,"type":205,"marks":224},"From airports and utilities to global manufacturers and financial institutions, On.Energy technology delivers stable, uninterrupted power in complex markets and challenging operating conditions where reliability matters most.",[225],{"type":208,"attrs":226},{"color":18},{"id":228,"alt":229,"name":18,"focus":230,"title":18,"source":18,"filename":231,"copyright":18,"fieldtype":188,"meta_data":232,"is_external_url":142},121205817850188,"Power Quality Hero","2657x1181:2658x1182","https://a.storyblok.com/f/288034353253643/4320x2430/44c6e495c8/power-quality-hero.jpg",{"alt":229,"title":18,"source":18,"copyright":18},"MC UPS™",[235,244,252,260,268,276],{"_uid":236,"copy":237,"logo":238,"component":243},"3ce5d3be-2d9c-4b6a-9d44-7f19db73b4a1","{{Citi Banamex}} is a leading financial institution in Mexico, where continuity, security, and uptime are non-negotiable. ON deployed behind-the-meter storage to strengthen onsite resilience—supporting stable power and reliable operations through grid disturbance and downtime ",{"id":239,"alt":240,"name":18,"focus":18,"title":18,"source":18,"filename":241,"copyright":18,"fieldtype":188,"meta_data":242,"is_external_url":142},111585904840576,"Citi","https://a.storyblok.com/f/288034353253643/330x46/b6951ac8fb/citi.svg",{"alt":240,"title":18,"source":18,"copyright":18},"expertise_project",{"_uid":245,"copy":246,"logo":247,"component":243},"66bd6608-ff99-4065-8451-e7a7448f7b1c","{{As one of the world’s largest retailers,}} Walmart operates high-throughput facilities where power quality and peak demand shape cost and reliability. ON deployed behind-the-meter storage to shift load and provide reactive power compensation—reducing peaks and stabilizing onsite power.",{"id":248,"alt":249,"name":18,"focus":18,"title":18,"source":18,"filename":250,"copyright":18,"fieldtype":188,"meta_data":251,"is_external_url":142},111585904844673,"Walmart","https://a.storyblok.com/f/288034353253643/330x28/6e20851c92/walmart.svg",{"alt":249,"title":18,"source":18,"copyright":18},{"_uid":253,"copy":254,"logo":255,"component":243},"201ea81c-81e4-498b-bd7e-c0e4a7c588c3","{{Grupo Bimbo is a global baking leader}} running continuous, automation-driven production where downtime is expensive. ON delivered behind-the-meter storage for load shifting and UPS support—protecting critical operations while optimizing how the site uses energy.",{"id":256,"alt":257,"name":18,"focus":18,"title":18,"source":18,"filename":258,"copyright":18,"fieldtype":188,"meta_data":259,"is_external_url":142},111585904881542,"Bimbo","https://a.storyblok.com/f/288034353253643/330x28/a80185bc2f/bimbo.svg",{"alt":257,"title":18,"source":18,"copyright":18},{"_uid":261,"copy":262,"logo":263,"component":243},"fd5f9117-10d1-45cb-b4bb-da968cbc0739","{{At ASUR’s Ciudad Juárez airport in Mexico}} we delivered a targeted optimization project combining load shifting and reactive compensation to lower peak costs, improve power factor, and enhance overall electrical stability",{"id":264,"alt":265,"name":18,"focus":18,"title":18,"source":18,"filename":266,"copyright":18,"fieldtype":188,"meta_data":267,"is_external_url":142},111585904869252,"Asur","https://a.storyblok.com/f/288034353253643/330x32/fa2cce166b/asur.svg",{"alt":265,"title":18,"source":18,"copyright":18},{"_uid":269,"copy":270,"logo":271,"component":243},"172a111e-99ab-4432-9e0c-e50aebf5996c","{{Enel is a global energy company}} operating generation and grid-scale infrastructure where reliability is non-negotiable. ON provided front-of-the-meter storage for backup—supporting grid resilience and dependable power when it matters most. ",{"id":272,"alt":273,"name":18,"focus":18,"title":18,"source":18,"filename":274,"copyright":18,"fieldtype":188,"meta_data":275,"is_external_url":142},111585904865155,"Enel","https://a.storyblok.com/f/288034353253643/330x32/a2f99a4c28/enel.svg",{"alt":273,"title":18,"source":18,"copyright":18},{"_uid":277,"copy":278,"logo":279,"component":243},"ec641356-1f15-4750-92e0-d77acd13fdcf","{{For OMA (Grupo Aeroportuario del Centro Norte)—}} an airport group that operates and manages 13 airports in Mexico with additional business lines across logistics, industrial parks, and hotels—we delivered an energy optimization project focused on load shifting and reactive power compensation to reduce peak demand exposure, improve power factor, and support more stable, efficient electrical operations",{"id":280,"alt":281,"name":18,"focus":18,"title":18,"source":18,"filename":282,"copyright":18,"fieldtype":188,"meta_data":283,"is_external_url":142},111585904856962,"Oma","https://a.storyblok.com/f/288034353253643/330x46/8dd82762cd/oma.svg",{"alt":281,"title":18,"source":18,"copyright":18},"expertise","Now deployed across dozens of industrial and enterprise campuses, MC UPS™ integrates with existing medium-voltage infrastructure to deliver flickerless, full-site power protection and multi-hour storage flexibility, combining uptime and grid participation in a single system.","{{When the grid falters,}} critical infrastructure can’t. Airports, manufacturers, and defense sites depend on uninterrupted power,  yet face instability that utilities can’t fix fast enough.","The Mission-Critical\nPower Quality Problem",[289,297,304,311,319],{"_uid":290,"image":291,"title":293,"component":296},"822e3d73-ef2f-4535-aa9e-7312acd485fd",{"id":292,"alt":293,"name":18,"focus":18,"title":18,"source":18,"filename":294,"copyright":18,"fieldtype":188,"meta_data":295,"is_external_url":142},119114754576684,"Hospitals","https://a.storyblok.com/f/288034353253643/3000x2329/f6db7a3c2a/hospitals.jpg",{"alt":293,"title":18,"source":18,"copyright":18},"expertise_industry",{"_uid":298,"image":299,"title":303,"component":296},"f91fa0ff-5478-49fc-b31b-5d7502c661db",{"id":300,"alt":293,"name":18,"focus":18,"title":18,"source":18,"filename":301,"copyright":18,"fieldtype":188,"meta_data":302,"is_external_url":142},119114754552107,"https://a.storyblok.com/f/288034353253643/3000x2000/f90dca6460/manufacturing.jpg",{"alt":293,"title":18,"source":18,"copyright":18},"Manufacturing",{"_uid":305,"image":306,"title":308,"component":296},"8f205223-ee61-4972-a472-8c515f85f823",{"id":307,"alt":308,"name":18,"focus":18,"title":18,"source":18,"filename":309,"copyright":18,"fieldtype":188,"meta_data":310,"is_external_url":142},119114754396455,"Water Systems","https://a.storyblok.com/f/288034353253643/3000x2246/ef38e30bf9/water-systems.jpg",{"alt":308,"title":18,"source":18,"copyright":18},{"_uid":312,"image":313,"title":318,"component":296},"325d9170-8cae-4857-bf2e-5f337e60c551",{"id":314,"alt":315,"name":18,"focus":18,"title":18,"source":18,"filename":316,"copyright":18,"fieldtype":188,"meta_data":317,"is_external_url":142},119114754380070,"Military & Defense","https://a.storyblok.com/f/288034353253643/3000x1997/1aeaa78ddb/military-defense.jpg",{"alt":315,"title":18,"source":18,"copyright":18},"Military & Defence",{"_uid":320,"image":321,"title":323,"component":296},"28def897-c702-405a-ab67-6eef05fc8d4f",{"id":322,"alt":323,"name":18,"focus":18,"title":18,"source":18,"filename":324,"copyright":18,"fieldtype":188,"meta_data":325,"is_ext