,"is_external_url":142},121197072856123,"OG Grid Volatility","https://a.storyblok.com/f/288034353253643/1200x630/fb1f39c13a/og-grid-volatility.jpg",{"alt":576,"title":18,"source":18,"copyright":18},"Grid Volatility Solutions | Distributed Storage in ERCOT | ON.energy","Turning volatility into value with distributed battery storage—charge low, discharge high, stabilize local nodes, and deliver top-tier performance in ERCOT.","bc94a398-72fb-4dce-aa7b-f296e56ed99e",{"type":196,"content":583},[584],{"type":211},{"id":586,"alt":587,"name":18,"focus":588,"title":18,"source":18,"filename":589,"copyright":18,"fieldtype":188,"meta_data":590,"is_external_url":142},121205817866573,"Grid Volatility Hero","3159x1310:3160x1311","https://a.storyblok.com/f/288034353253643/4320x2430/1c8efb7dd7/grid-volatility-hero.jpg",{"alt":587,"title":18,"source":18,"copyright":18},"IPP",[],"ON solves the grid’s flexibility challenge through deployment, not theory. Applying technology, regulatory know-how, and private capital to build assets that strengthen reliability and accelerate the energy transition.","{{ERCOT,}} the Texas power market, is the fastest-growing and most unpredictable in the U.S. We built one of the largest distributed storage platforms in the region to turn volatility into value and deliver reliable power where it’s needed most","Solving for\nGrid Volatility",[],"{{Electric demand is rising faster than infrastructure can follow}} Thin reserves and stalled interconnections now define most power markets. Renewables are plentiful, but flexibility is scarce, and that’s where the opportunity lies.",[599,608],{"_uid":600,"copy":601,"image":602,"title":607,"component":339},"3b5063b6-52c5-4332-8b14-6d44d9ba19a6","MWh delivering stability.",{"id":603,"alt":604,"name":18,"focus":18,"title":18,"source":18,"filename":605,"copyright":18,"fieldtype":188,"meta_data":606,"is_external_url":142},119116412535798,"Grid Volatility returns","https://a.storyblok.com/f/288034353253643/1408x736/09a18